@Node "yuvn.datatype()" "yuvn.datatype/yuvn.datatype"

@{b}    NAME@{ub}
	yuvn.datatype -- data type for yuvn and vlab pictures.

@{b}    FUNCTION@{ub}
	The yuvn data type, a sub-class of the @{"picture.datatype" Link "picture_dtc/picture.datatype()"}, is used
	to load yuvn/vlab files.

@{b}    METHODS@{ub}
	OM_NEW -- Create a new picture object from a yuvn or vlab file. The source
	   can either be DTST_FILE or DTST_CLIPBOARD.

